# Summary & Recommendations
  The $20 / 30-day investment produced **exceptional productivity**: substantial progress on a complex core app (CryptoChess with PQC/crypto features) through multiple specialized conversations, plus practical supporting tools, widgets, optimizations, and planning. Prompt efficiency appears strong, with the CryptoChess-related work likely offering the best "features per prompt" ratio due to its depth and iterations.

  **Overall verdict**: Outstanding value. The cost per app/task is tiny (~$1–2.50), while the delivered functionality, refinements, and supporting work represent thousands of dollars in equivalent effort. This demonstrates highly effective AI-augmented development.

